#
# package devel
#
##############################################################################

#package devel
#Summary: Development files for %{pkgname}
#Group: Applications/System
#description devel
#Development files for %{pkgname}.

#files devel

# Your development files go here
# Programmers documentation goes here
#doc doc

# end of file
